  "remarks": "\n Aleksandrov Scientific Research Technological Institute NITI is involved in designing, testing, and supporting nuclear power and naval propulsion reactors as well as their systems and parts. Aleksandrov Scientific Research Technological Institute NITI is an involved person under regulation 6(2)(a)(ii) and 6(4)(c) of Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulation 2019 because it is carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, the energy sector. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
